# COVID-19 Analysis Project

## Project Overview
This project analyzes COVID-19 data through three stages:

### Stage 1: Data Collection and Exploration
- Data acquisition
- Data cleaning
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

Files:
- Notebook: Stage-1/notebooks/covid_stage1.ipynb
- Presentation: Stage-1/presentation/Stage1_Presentation.pptx

### Stage 2: Advanced Analysis and Visualization
- Trend analysis
- Geographic analysis
- Statistical insights

Files:
- Notebook: Stage-2/notebooks/covid_stage2.ipynb
- Presentation: Stage-2/presentation/Stage2_Presentation.pptx

### Stage 3: Predictive Modeling and Conclusions
- Forecasting
- Model evaluation
- Final recommendations

Files:
- Notebook: Stage-3/notebooks/covid_stage3.ipynb
- Presentation: Stage-3/presentation/Stage3_Presentation.pptx

